50|$|Together with Australia and Korea, the Philippines Office for Transport Security (OTS) {{conducted}} a workshop on how <b>airport</b> <b>design</b> {{can help to}} develop security for staff, airlines and travellers. The Philippines Government allocated considerable funding {{for the improvement of}} 24 airports and the renovation of numerous international terminals across the country. These works are required to integrate new aviation security standards and infrastructure.|$|E
